    style 50 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    51("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Signing / Key service</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>KMS or Fulcio (keyless CA)<br />that houba's attestor uses to<br />sign in-toto attestations<br />(DSSE). Trust is org<br />configuration, not baked in.</div>")
    style 51 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
